test_cases.steps:
1. Via API — POST /api/vacation/v1/sick-leaves as creator with login=target's login
   Body: {login: '<target>', startDate: '<future>', endDate: '<future+5>', force: false}
2. Verify HTTP 200 — sick leave created
3. Verify the sick leave is for the target employee, not the creator
DB-CHECK: SELECT sl.employee, e.login FROM ttt_vacation.sick_leave sl JOIN ttt_vacation.employee e ON sl.employee = e.id WHERE sl.id = <created_id>
CLEANUP: Via API — DELETE /api/vacation/v1/sick-leaves/{id}
